  "title": "Construction Management",
  "description": "<p>Assist the project manager in coordinating day-to-day site operations</p><p>Monitor construction progress to ensure compliance with drawings and schedules</p><p>Manage workers, subcontractors, and suppliers at the site and assign tasks accordingly</p><p>Ensure site safety and compliance with Workplace Safety and Health (WSH) regulations</p><p>Maintain site records and conduct quality inspections; report issues in a timely manner</p><p>Oversee material deliveries and arrange for proper use of site equipment</p><p>Liaise with clients, consultants, and other stakeholders to resolve site-related issues</p><p>Able to communicate in English, Chinese, and Bengali</p>",
